Name: Wei Hern Lim
COM S 327 Assignment 2

This is a basic snake game written in C++ using the ncurses library.

Objective
Collect as many apples (a) as possible.

Rules
You cannot hit the surrounding walls or your own tail.

Instructions
Once you run the makefile, you can start the game by typing ./snake
There are 3 difficulties to choose from: easy, medium, hard
You can choose the difficulty by adding a flag before launching the game, eg: ./snake easy
The default difficulty is medium
Once you start the game, hit any button to begin

Controls
w: move up
a: move left
s: move down
d: move right
q: quit game

